The paper proposes a framework for transfer learning using pre-trained deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs) for visual recognition tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the focus is on transfer learning using pre-trained CNNs, cs.LG and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories.
